chemical, uh, substances.

01:16:41.160 --> 01:16:44.038
- Prescription drugs.
- Prescription drugs.

01:17:22.280 --> 01:17:26.910
"To neither love
nor reverence wilt thou be kind,

01:17:27.000 --> 01:17:31.437
"and even for hate thou canst but kill,

01:17:31.520 --> 01:17:33.670
