01:17:35.720 --> 01:17:37.199
I like it.

01:17:37.280 --> 01:17:39.669
It's got that what-a-cruel-world

01:17:39.760 --> 01:17:44.197
so let's-toss-ourselves-in-the-abyss
type of ambiance, huh?

01:17:46.000 --> 01:17:48.992
Come on. It's Heather's copy of Moby Dick.

01:17:51.280 --> 01:17:54.238
Why don't you give it a try?
Underline something.

01:17:56.240 --> 01:17:58.834
Get off of my bed, you fucking psycho!

01:17:58.920 --> 01:18:02.799
You think you're a rebel?
Do you actually think you're a rebel?

01:18:02.880 --> 01:18:05.792
You're not a rebel.
You're fucking psychotic.

01:18:07.520 --> 01:18:10.034
You say "tom-ay-to", I say "tom-ah-to".

01:18:10.120 --> 01:18:12.031
Hold it.

01:18:12.120 --> 01:18:15.351
Eskimo. Look at that.

01:18:16.440 --> 01:18:19.034
That's one word. I love it!

01:18:19.120 --> 01:18:23.511
I usually go for the whole sentence myself
but this is perfecto.

01:18:23.600 --> 01:18:27.275
Eskimo, you know, it's so, uh, mysterious.

01:18:28.480 --> 01:18:31.995
Eskimo.

01:18:36.640 --> 01:18:38.596
Come on.

01:18:40.280 --> 01:18:42.475
JD, you are not listening to me.

01:18:43.520 --> 01:18:45.988
Nag. Nag. Nag. Nag. Nag!

01:18:47.800 --> 01:18:50.075
Th-th-that knife is filthy.

01:18:50.160 --> 01:18:53.675
